snippet.title: Ghosts 'n Goblins Resurrection - Pre-order Trailer
snippet.description:
Are you prepared to CHALLENGE AGAIN? Ghosts ‘n Goblins Resurrection launches on Nintendo Switch on February 25th! Pre-order today to begin your knight’s journey as soon as the game is available! https://bit.ly/GnGRPreorder
